                  data-feather="inbox" class="w-l5"></i></div>
        <h4 class="white fw-600 fs-m3 mb-5">Discover Skills</h4>
        <div class="indigo-lightest fw-600 fs-m1 lh-3 opacity-50">Explore a diverse range of talents from our vibrant community. Find the skill you want to learn and the expert who can teach you.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-100pc md-w-40pc">
      <div class="br-8 p-5 m-5">
