                  data-feather="cpu" class="w-l5"></i></div>
        <h4 class="white fw-600 fs-m3 mb-5">Connect with Experts</h4>
        <div class="indigo-lightest fw-600 fs-m1 opacity-50">Engage with professionals and enthusiasts alike. Build your network by connecting with peers who share your passion for learning and growth.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-100pc md-w-40pc">
      <div class="br-8 p-5 m-5">
        <div class="flex justify-center items-center bg-indigo-lightest-10 white w-l5 h-l5 br-round mb-5"><i
                  data-feather="database" class="w-l5"></i></div>
        <h4 class="white fw-600 fs-m3 mb-5">Exchange Knowledge</h4>
        <div class="indigo-lightest fw-600 fs-m1 opacity-50">Offer your expertise in one area in exchange for knowledge in another. Grow together by teaching and learning with fellow skill swappers.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- big text -->
<section class="p-10 md-py-10">
